<plot>In this short allegory, the Israeli-Palestinian conflict in the Middle East plays itself out on a smaller scale, as a plate of hotly contested hummus is placed between an Israeli and a Palestinian at a dinner party. Although 'Conflict in a Middle Table' is a comedy, it presents serious and complex ideological issues.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?113958</url></doc>
